name: Luna Kindred 月下初擁 | Honkai Impact 3rd
description:
.

v5 contains both outfits

luna_kindred_l_v8-000015 only has outfit "luna_kindred"

luna_kindred_r_v2-000025 only has outfit "rosy_bridesmaid"

.

The last two one slightly improved the overfitting issue in v5, and applied multires noise in training.

.

Luna Kindred from Honkai Impact 3

崩壞三的月下初擁

.

There are two sets of outfits, can be chosen by trigger words

有兩套服裝，用提示詞選擇

.

The two outfits are "Luna Kindred" and "Rosy Bridesmaid"

兩套服裝分別為｢月下初擁｣、｢花裳月紗｣

.

No outfit "Before the Dawn", since I can't find enough image

沒有｢夜明之前｣，因為找不到圖

.

月下我婆

.
